Feb 9 (Reuters) - Competition and Markets Authority:

  • UK CMA: INDUSTRY RULES SETTING OUT HOW GROCERY RETAILERS SHOULD TREAT THEIR SUPPLIERS WILL NOW APPLY TO AMAZON

  • CMA: AMAZON AND ITS RELEVANT UK SUBSIDIARIES MUST NOW COMPLY WITH GROCERIES SUPPLY CODE OF PRACTICE ( CODE)
